Photo: Rich Barnes, Getty Images Image 26 of 26 U.S. Women's National Soccer team to play at Alamodome in December 1 / 26 Back to Gallery SAN ANTONIO — The U.S. Women's National Soccer Team will face Trinidad and Tobago at the Alamodome on Dec. 10 as part of its "Victory Tour" for the FIFA World Cup.
The U.S. crushed Japan 2015 in July's final to claim its third World Cup championship. It will mark the USWNT's third appearance in San Antonio, following a 4-0 triumph over Australia in 2013 in front of nearly 20,000 at the Alamodome.
